STEPS:
1) sudo apt update
2) sudo apt install qemu-kvm
3) sudo apt install libvirt-daemon-system libvirt-clients
4) sudo adduser $USER kvm
5) reboot
6) sudo apt install virt-manager -y
7) Download an Ubuntu iso file(Ubuntu16 - recommended)Open Virtual Machine Manager and install KVM Machine
8) Wait to finish installation and then run any commands don't close machine by any chance.
